000 observations only the k=9 mode displays clear normal\ntriplet structure. Even though the pulsation amplitudes change on timescales of\ndays and years, the eigenfrequencies remain essentially the same, showing the\nstellar structure is not changing on any dynamical timescale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2003 18:45:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
