nian system we find that it experiences a\nKAM breakdown for $\\eta \\simeq 0.26$: above which the near integrable regions\ndegenerate into chaos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2003 23:45:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
